Caption: Dignitaries seated amongst the audience at the stadium
Description: Sitting in the first row, from left: Mr. R. Natarajan, Registrar (third from left), Mansoor Ali Khan (Nawab of Pataudi), captain of the Indian cricket team (fourth from left), Prof. P. C. Varghese (fifth from left) and Mr. Y. S. Ramaswamy (seventh from left in first row).
